  "rationale": "Repair: the only accent on the page now lives on the hero's colossal display-title, and the hero is the single inverse (bookend) section \u2014 every other section is on the cream primary surface with no accent element, satisfying single-accent. Order follows the brief's scroll: an inverse hero bookend (sanctioned display-title-over-media + media-over-media overlap), an anchored ABOUT manifesto with a ghost word, a full-bleed gallery band with static counter + marginal caption, a mirrored mission statement (stagger), a novel 1941/2023 heritage timeline using a stat-block run behind an era ghost word, the seeded curator quote + portrait collage, a visit split pairing address/hours with the real Map.jpg and a typographic Buy-tickets link (no button), an underline-only newsletter form, and a slash-nav footer. Off-grid treatments (overlap, bleed, stagger, ghost-word) are used per the unlocked editorial style; all media reference only real brand assets."
